{"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate\/mapview:viewforannotation:"]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate\/mapView:viewForAnnotation:"},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)MLNAnnotationView","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"MLNAnnotationView"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(cs)MLNMapView","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"MLNMapView"},{"kind":"text","text":" *) "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"mapView"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"viewForAnnotation:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:Qoobjc(pl)MLNAnnotation","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"id<MLNAnnotation>"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"annotation"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The map view that requested the annotation view."}]}],"name":"mapView"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The object representing the annotation that is about to be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"displayed."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"annotation"}]},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Return Value","anchor":"return-value"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The view object to display for the given annotation or "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"nil"},{"type":"text","text":" if you"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"want to display an annotation image instead."}]}],"kind":"content"},{"content":[{"type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Implement this method to mark a point annotation with a view object. If you"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"want to mark a particular point annotation with a static image instead, omit"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"this method or have it return "},{"code":"nil","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" for that annotation, then implement"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"-mapView:imageForAnnotation:","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" instead."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Annotation views are compatible with UIKit, Core Animation, and other Cocoa"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Touch frameworks. On the other hand, static annotation images use less memory"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"and draw more quickly than annotation views."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The user location annotation view can also be customized via this method. When"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"annotation","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" is an instance of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocation","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" (or equal to the map view’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"code":"userLocation","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" property), return an instance of "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocationAnnotationView","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"(or a subclass thereof)."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","level":4,"anchor":"Related-examples","text":"Related examples"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"TODO: Add annotation views and images, learn how to specify what"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" to use for a given "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object on your"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"map."}],"type":"paragraph"}],"kind":"content"}],"sections":[],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns a view object to mark the given point annotation object on the map."}],"metadata":{"externalID":"c:objc(pl)MLNMapViewDelegate(im)mapView:viewForAnnotation:","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"roleHeading":"Instance Method","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"mapView:viewForAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"role":"symbol","remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNMapViewDelegate.h#L742","fileName":"MLNMapViewDelegate.h"},"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"mapView:viewForAnnotation:","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"mapView:viewForAnnotation:","symbolKind":"method"},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapViewDelegate":{"title":"MLNMapViewDelegate","type":"topic","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate","type":"reference"},{"text":" protocol defines a set of optional methods that you","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"can use to receive map-related update messages. Because many map operations","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"require the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView","type":"reference"},{"text":" class to load data asynchronously, the map view calls","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"these methods to notify your application when specific operations complete. The","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"map view also uses these methods to request information about annotations","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"displayed on the map, such as the styles and interaction modes to apply to","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"individual annotations.","type":"text"}],"role":"symbol","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapViewDelegate","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"},{"text":" class is responsible for marking a point annotation","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"object that corresponds to the ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"text":" protocol. When an annotation’s","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"offscreen.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview","role":"symbol","title":"MLNAnnotationView","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotationView"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNUserLocation":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The MLNUserLocation class defines a specific type of annotation that identifies"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the user’s current location. You do not create instances of this class"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"directly. Instead, you retrieve an existing "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocation"},{"type":"text","text":" object from the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"userLocation"},{"type":"text","text":" property of the map view displayed in your application."}],"title":"MLNUserLocation","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocation","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnuserlocation","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNUserLocation"}],"kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"title":"MapLibre","role":"collection"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapViewDelegate/mapView:viewForAnnotation:":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapviewdelegate\/mapview:viewforannotation:","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:viewForAnnotation:"}],"title":"mapView:viewForAnnotation:","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Returns a view object to mark the given point annotation object on the map."}],"role":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"mapView:viewForAnnotation:"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapViewDelegate\/mapView:viewForAnnotation:","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"MLNAnnotation","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNUserLocationAnnotationView":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNUserLocationAnnotationView"}],"title":"MLNUserLocationAnnotationView","type":"topic","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnuserlocationannotationview","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"View representing an "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocation"},{"type":"text","text":" on screen."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocationAnnotationView","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNMapView":{"title":"MLNMapView","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"An interactive, customizable map view with an interface similar to the one"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"provided by Apple’s MapKit."}],"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnmapview","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNMapView","kind":"identifier"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNMapView"}}}